# TOOLS.md - Local Tool Notes

This file stores environment-specific tool notes. Keep it free of secrets.

## Runtime

- Gateway: `http://127.0.0.1:8000`
- Health: `GET /health`
- Runtime config: `~/.synapse/synapse.json`
- Runtime workspace: `~/.synapse/workspace`

## Style

- Use tools when they materially help.
- Prefer local/private tools when available.
- Do not leak raw diagnostics into messaging channels.
- Ask before external side effects or sensitive data transmission.

## Local Notes

Add device names, voice IDs, browser details, SSH aliases, and other safe local
setup notes here.
